.br
      unsigned long *\fIlength\fP;
.br
      int *\fIformat\fP;
.FN
.IP \fIw\fP 1i
Specifies the widget that requested the selection value.
.IP \fIclient_data\fP 1i
Specifies a value passed in by the widget when it requested the
