.LP
When the configureHook callbacks are called, the \fItype\fP is
.PN XtHconfigure ,
\fIwidget\fP is the widget being configured, and \fIchangeMask\fP and 
\fIchanges\fP reflect the changes made to the widget. The callbacks 
